
Q2. How to add an image in the pygame window?  Fill the missing step in blank line:
   
    Myimage = pygame.image.load ("bg2.jpg").convert()
     screen.fill((0,0,0))
    screen,blit(Myimage,[0,0])
_________________________?        

pygame.image.upload()
pygame.display.update()
pygame.display.show()
pygame.showimage()


Q5.  How to make conditions to check whether the triangle is isosceles or not.
  (Hint:-  Suppose there are A,B,C sides are given for triangle, for a isosceles triangle any two sides must be equal.)


if (A==B or B==C or A==C)
if(A==B==C)
if(A==B,A==C)
if(A=B,A=C,B=C)

 Solution
 A=5
 B=10
 C=10
 < condition here>:
   print ("Triangle is Isoscele");
else:
print ("Triangle is not isoscele")

